			SystemTrayN
			A notification area applet for ROX-Filer
			by Andy Hanton and Stephen Watson

31-Dec-2007 (0.3.3)
~~~~~~~~~~~
Fixes for 0compile support (reported by Thomas Leonard).

04-Aug-2007
~~~~~~~~~~~
Ensure write permission when using 0compile.

11-Jul-2007 (0.3.2)
~~~~~~~~~~~
Allow use of 0compile.

29-Dec-2006
~~~~~~~~~~~
Translate strings in Options.xml, using the method in ROX-Filer.

28-Aug-2006
~~~~~~~~~~~
Partially reverted to old way to set minimum size, due to what I think is
a limitation in GTK.

24-Aug-2006
~~~~~~~~~~~
Better way of enforcing a minimum size.  Minimum size is now an option.

07-Aug-2006
~~~~~~~~~~~
Fix positioning of message window.

11-Feb-2006 (0.3.1)
~~~~~~~~~~~
Fix for menu shortcuts.

21-Jan-2006
~~~~~~~~~~~
Add injector feed.  Fix parsing of options.  Added support for menu
shortcuts.

20-Jan-2006
~~~~~~~~~~~
Updates for current ROX-CLib practice: use libdir to find ROX-CLib,
use rox_init_with_domain(), add Zero Install target to Makefile.
May need to explicitly link against libX11, added configure test.
Don't use guchar for strings, just causes gcc warnings.

14-Jan-2006 (0.3)
~~~~~~~~~~~
Maintainance (unilateraly) taken over by Stephen Watson.

22-Oct-2005
~~~~~~~~~~~
Updated for ROX-CLib changes (Stephen Watson).

14-July-2003 (Release 0.2)
~~~~~~~~~~~~
Fixed support for gtk 2.0
Added icon (Alexey Lubimov).
Added a seperator in front of the icons (Alexey Lubimov).
Added Russian Translation (Alexey Lubimov).
